transcripts.text: Lindsey Graham isn't the same.  He's changed.  After 25 years, he's become another phony D.C.  politician who would do anything to hold on to power.  He's not working for South Carolina or us.  He will take away our health care and end protections for people with pre-existing conditions, even COVID.  Let's elect someone with integrity, a leader, organizer, and activist from our community.  Vote Jamie Harrison for Senate.
